2026-04-16 20:54:16 - llm.aliyun_llm - INFO - 收到 LLM API 响应  result={'choices': [{'message': {'content': '', 'reasoning_content': "The init_project was successful. Now I need to:\n1. Write the requirements to /mnt/shared/needs/requirements.md\n2. Send a task_assign email to PM\n3. Confirm the email was written to PM's mailbox\n\nLet me proceed with step 2 - writing the requirements file. I need to use the write-output skill or I can use init_project's sandbox to write the file. Actually, looking at the agent_rules, I should write the requirements using a bash command in the sandbox. But I need to use skill_loader for all operations.\n\nLet me use write-output skill to write the requirements file, and then use mailbox skill to send the email.\n\nActually, I can do both steps in parallel since they don't depend on each other - writing the requirements file and sending the email. Wait, actually the email references the requirements file path, but the email content is just a path reference, not the actual content. So I can send both in parallel.\n\nBut actually, I should make sure the requirements file is written first before sending the email, because the PM needs to be able to read it. Though the email just contains a path reference, so technically they could be done in parallel. But to be safe, let me write the requirements first, then send the email.\n\nLet me write the requirements file first using write-output skill.", 'role': 'assistant', 'tool_calls': [{'function': {'arguments': '{"skill_name": "write-output", "task_context": "将项目需求文档写入 /mnt/shared/needs/requirements.md。内容如下：\\n\\n# 项目需求：XiaoPaw 宠物健康记录功能\\n\\n## 项目背景\\n\\nXiaoPaw 是一款宠物管理应用，用户当前可以记录宠物基本信息（名字、品种、年龄）。\\n本次需求：新增宠物健康记录功能，让用户能追踪宠物的疫苗接种和就医记录。\\n\\n## 功能需求\\n\\n### F-01：疫苗记录\\n- 用户可以添加宠物的疫苗接种记录（疫苗名称、接种日期、下次到期日）\\n- 用户可以查看宠物的历史疫苗记录列表\\n- 临近到期（30天内）时，在宠物主页显示提醒标识\\n\\n### F-02：就医记录\\n- 用户可以添加就医记录（日期、医院名称、就医原因、诊断结果、费用）\\n- 用户可以查看历史就医记录，支持按日期排序\\n- 就医记录支持添加备注（最多 500 字）\\n\\n## 验收标准（DoD）\\n\\n1. 用户可以为每只宠物独立管理健康记录（不同宠物数据不互相干扰）\\n2. 所有记录持久化存储，App 重启后数据不丢失\\n3. 疫苗到期提醒在宠物主页正确显示（到期日期在 30 天内）\\n4. 就医记录按日期倒序展示（最新记录在最前）\\n5. 产品文档必须包含：产品概述 + 用户故事 + 功能规格 + 验收标准\\n\\n## 优先级\\n\\nP0（本次必须交付）：F-01 疫苗记录 + F-02 就医记录核心流程\\nP1（可延后）：批量导入历史记录、数据导出功能\\n\\n输出文件路径：/mnt/shared/needs/requirements.md"}', 'name': 'skill_loader'}, 'id': 'tool-390ded7ea91a4a4790336c02dbc3fbcd', 'index': 0, 'type': 'function'}]}, 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'index': 0, 'logprobs': None}], 'object': 'chat.completion', 'usage': {'prompt_tokens': 4431, 'completion_tokens': 648, 'total_tokens': 5079, 'completion_tokens_details': {'reasoning_tokens': 273}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 4223}}, 'created': 1776344056, 'system_fingerprint': None, 'model': 'glm-5.1', 'id': 'chatcmpl-24b029e6-8d0e-996c-a00e-2932d9618676'}
